<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200812/34edcdc627e646ada42f51760dc987fe.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">成套矿业机械设备在矿区施工</span></img></p>
